This file encodes the current knowledge about the isomorphism types
of Singer algebras A[q,z] with z <= 10000.
The entry for z has the form '[ z, [ L_1, L_2, ... ] ]' where each L_i
is a sorted list of nonnegative integers describing smallest
representatives q that belong to isomorphic algebras, except that the
first entry 0 in L_i means that the isomorphism question for the other
entries in L_i is not yet decided.
